snippet.title: Gunship X -- Announce Trailer | PS4, PS Vita
snippet.description:
Danger and death are plaguing the ground. Innocent people run for their lives. It's time for you to step in and do something about it. Dispense destruction from the skies and obliterate the enemy. Coming to PS4 and PS Vita in 2015

http://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/gunship-x-psvita/
